---
title: Mediterranean Lamb Meatballs with Creamy Pesto Dressing & Garden Salad
description: For meatballs with some Mediterranean vibes, lace them with our rich herb seasoning. Then add an extra layer of flavour by coating them
in our onion chutney before serving over a simple and textural salad to balance out the richness. Don't forget the drizzle of creamy basil
pesto dressing to tie everything together.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving and under 30g carbohydrates per serving.*
